25. The system of claim 20 further comprising a second flow control device adapted for fluid communication with the water source, said device comprising 
a third pipe including a second plurality of elongated inlets; 
a fourth pipe including a second plurality of outlets in fluid communication with a second plurality of ports; and 
at least one of said third pipe and said fourth pipe being movable, one relative to the other, among a second plurality of positions; 
wherein at least one elongated inlet of said second plurality of elongated inlets is in fluid communication with at least one outlet of said second plurality of outlets through said second plurality of positions.
